Specifies the program use to edit files when
the
.B -Edit
option is used.
(See also the
.I EDITOR
environment variable.)
Defaults to
.I vi
if not set.
See the \fIvisual_\%command\fP fields in \fIaeuconf\fP(1) for how to
override this specifically for Aegis.
